UMHOLI we-EFF uMnuz Julius Malema uyihlabe wayihlikiza inkulumo kamengameli wase-United States, uMnuz Donald Trump, othe uzolufakela izibuko udaba lokudliwa komhlaba kuleli.UMalema uphawule ngalolu daba esithangameni nabezindaba ngoLwesine lapho eveze khona ukuthi iNingizimu Afrika isazobhekana nobunzima odabeni lomhlaba. Uthe inkulumo kaTrump ayimethusi nakancane ngoba ubeyilindele kumuntu ofana naye.“Uma kuwukuthi abantu bakuleli abakazimiseli ukudla umhlaba ngoba besaba unswinyo nokugxekwa, akumele bavotele i-EFF. Uma besivotela thina sizowudla umhlaba futhi uDonald Trump, iBritain ne-European Union bazosihlasela ngalokho. Ngihlezi ngisho ukuthi ngaphambi kokuzuza okuhle, kuqala izinhlungu. Uma abantu bakuleli bengazimesele ngokudlula ezinhlungwini, abakhohlwe umhlaba. UDonald Trump akakasho lutho, kusazoza izinkinga zangempela,” kusho uMalema.FUNDA:
 UTrump uthi uzolufakela izibuko oloMhlaba eNingizimu AfrikaUMalema uqhube wathi labo ababeseka owayengumengameli wakuleli, uMnuz Jacob Zuma, kwi-ANC okuyibo abahambisana nokudliwa komhlaba ngaphandle kwesinxephezelo bayazazi izingqinamba izwe lakuleli elisazodlula kuzo odabeni lomhlaba.“Sizimisele ukufa ngodaba lomhlaba. Okwesibili esizimisele ngakho ukuhlupheka ngoba siyazi bazovala ompompi (bomnotho). Kumele silungiselele yonke into, ngisho impi. Kumele sizilungiselele uDonald Trump nabo bonke, asibesaba. Usivuselele ugqozi kakhulu ngemuva kombhalo wakhe kuTwitter,” kusho uMalema.I have asked Secretary of State 
@SecPompeo to closely study the South Africa land and farm seizures and expropriations and the large scale killing of farmers. “South African Government is now seizing land from white farmers.” 
