March 24, 2019Iqhube yaxwayisa nokho ukuthi ukunqanyuswa kukagesi akukapheli njengoba isalungisa isimo. I-Eskom ithe ugesi uzonqamuka uma kunesimo esiphoqayo.Ukunqanyula kukagesi ngeledlule kuthakameze izimpilo zabaningi kuleli ngokunjalo nomnotho wakuleli. Ungqongqoshe amaBhizinisi kaHulumeni, uMnuz Pravin Gordhan, nosihlalo webhodi le-Eskom, uMnuz Jabu Mabuza, bathe inkinga yokunqanyulwa kukagesi idalwa wukungalungiswa kweziteshi ezineminyaka ewu-35 zasungulwa.“Kuphele iminyaka eminingi iziteshi zikagesi zingalungiswa. Umbuzo wukuthi, ngabe imali yokulungisa iziteshi ibiyenziwani? Iziteshi ezintsha zikagesi okuyiMedupi neKusile azikasebenzi. Iqiniso wukuthi ingqalasizinda yethu iyawa ngenxa yokuthi ibingalungiswa,” kusho uMabuza.UGordhan uthe kuyishwa ukuthi i-Eskom ibingabatsheli zonke izinkinga zayo abantu kodwa uzokwenza isiqiniseko sokuthi ezinsukwini eziwu-14 ezizayo abantu batshelwa konke okwenzekayo.IDA ngakolunye uhlangothi kule mpelasonto ithe izinkinga ze-Eskom zidalwe yinkohlakalo.“Imibiko yokuthi imali okwakumele isetshenziselwe ukugcina iziteshi eziphehla amandla zisesimeni zahanjiswa ngobukhonyovu eKusile Powe Station nakwezinye izinhlelo okwadliwa ngazo imali ngamathenda ayekhishwa,” kusho okhulumela iDA esitatimendeni uNksz Natasha Mazzone.

UMQEQESHI we-Orlando Pirates, uMilutin "Micho" Sredojevic, uzifuna zonke izicoco ezisele kule sizini.Lokhu kuvele exoxa nabezindaba ngemuva kokudlulela kuma-semi final e-2018 Telkom Knockout.EzikaMicho zinqobe ngo 3-1 eMoses Mabhida Stadium, eThekwini."Yonke imidlalo esiyidlalayo kwi-Orlando Pirates sidlala sengathi ngeyokugcina," kusho uSredojevic."Kuyimanje abalandeli bethu baya emakhaya. Bathembile. NgoLwesibili sinePolokwane City, omunye umdlalo omkhulu neqembu elinzima."UMicho ucule iculo elihlukile ukunabanye abaqeqeshi base-Europe ngokushaya izitayela kwabadlali bakhe ngemuva kokushaya igoli lesithathu."Ibhola silidlalela abalandeli, uma kufanele sishaye izitayela ukuze sibabonge ngokuseseka siqnobe ngale ndlela, sizokwenza lokho," ksuho uMicho%%%twitter https://twitter.com/hashtag/TKO2018?src=hash&ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#TKO2018
